title: Sawbones: The HPV Vaccine
description:
A vaccine that can practically eliminate a type of human cancer should be cause for celebration across our species. Would it surprise it to learn that some people don't trust it? ... Probably not at this point, huh?

This week on Sawbones: The HPV vaccine.

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
